Ppxlib integration and OCaml AST construction utilities.

{1 Synopsis}

This module provides helper functions for constructing OCaml Parsetree nodes
using Ppxlib's Ast_builder. It abstracts common patterns and provides
convenient builders for generating well-formed OCaml AST during the conversion
from SML.

{1 Key Components}

- {!Builder} - Core AST construction utilities using Ppxlib
- Ghost location handling for generated code
- Type-safe AST node creation

